'''黎明'''{{SBS}}{{MH}}（{{lang-en|Leon Lai Ming}}；{{bd|1966年|12月11日||catIdx=L黎}}），是一名[[香港|香港]]歌手及演員，出生於[[北京|北京]]，兒時隨父親移民香港，曾留學於英國，他在1986年參加《[[第五屆新秀歌唱大賽|第五屆新秀歌唱大賽]]》獲獎後從事演員工作，其後於1990年成為歌手<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |author = 梁慧琳 |url = https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20160509/19603391 |title = 開show過後無艇搭 天王的滄海遺珠 |publisher = 蘋果日報 |date = 2016-05-09 |accessdate = 2018-12-29 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181109234659/https://hk.lifestyle.appledaily.com/lifestyle/special/daily/article/20160509/19603391 |archive-date = 2018-11-09 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，自1992年開始被傳媒譽為「[[香港四大天王|四大天王]]」之一。1999年，黎明宣佈退出香港地區的音樂頒獎禮，以投入更多時間發展音樂和電影事業，其後於2002年憑電影《[[三更之回家|三更之回家]]》獲得[[金馬獎最佳男主角|金馬獎最佳男主角]]，並於2004年與[[林建岳|林建岳]]合作成立唱片公司[[A_Music|A Music]]，參與音樂及電影的投資和製作<ref name="陳善之">{{Cite book |author = 陳善之、翟浩然 |title = 善緣滿佈—陳善之回首前塵四十載 |location = 香港 |publisher = 明窗出版社 |date = 2016 |ISBN = 9888338684 |language = zh}}</ref>。黎明歷年來參與過不同機構的慈善及公益活動，他在1994年接受[[聯合國兒童基金會|聯合國兒童基金會]]的委任，成為全球首個華人「國際愛心大使」並持有[[聯合國通行證|領事級護照]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://i.imgur.com/K5NyuYa.jpg |title = 國際愛心大使黎明 sell愛的朱古力 |date = 1994-08-09 |publisher = 新電視1072期 |language = zh |accessdate = 2022-06-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220626023905/https://i.imgur.com/K5NyuYa.jpg |archive-date = 2022-06-26 |dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/fqfy5Ss.jpg |title = 聯合國兒童基金會頒領事級護照 黎明以歌手身分獲殊榮 |publisher = 明報 |date = 1994-11-14 |accessdate = 2022-06-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220626014714/https://i.imgur.com/fqfy5Ss.jpg |archive-date = 2022-06-26 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，翌年晉升為「國際青年特使」，創下了慈善活動受惠人數最多的[[健力士世界紀錄|健力士世界紀錄]]<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/FFlmlHo.jpg |title = 黎明名登健力氏 升為國際青年特使 |publisher = 電視日報 |date = 1995-12-01 |accessdate = 2021-12-05 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211205043028/https://i.imgur.com/FFlmlHo.jpg |archive-date = 2021-12-17 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。1998年，黎明獲選為[[香港十大傑出青年|香港十大傑出青年]]<ref name="十大傑出青年">{{cite news |language = zh |author = 依玲 |url = https://i.imgur.com/vc8jZxX.jpg |title = 黎明當選傑青遺憾讀書少 |publisher = 明報 |date = 1998-10-11 |accessdate = 2021-05-24 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210524130007/https://i.imgur.com/vc8jZxX.jpg |archive-date = 2021-05-24 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，其後在2003年至2019年間三度獲[[香港特別行政區政府|香港特別行政區政府]]授勳<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1632874/ |title = 3度授勳 黎明獲頒銀紫荊星章：多謝大家給予機會 |publisher = 頭條日報 |date = 2019-11-09 |accessdate = 2020-02-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191109120938/http://hd.stheadline.com/life/ent/realtime/1632874/即時-娛樂-3度授勳-黎明獲頒銀紫荊星章-多謝大家給予機會 |archive-date = 2019-11-09 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，現為[[香港公益金|香港公益金]]名譽副會長。

== 個人背景 ==
黎明於1966年12月11日在北京出生，母親原欲取名「黎捷」，父親黎新生則認為「黎明」讀音較響亮，遂以此定名<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = http://hk.crntt.com/crn-webapp/doc/docDetailCreate.jsp?coluid=21&kindid=267&docid=100067542&mdate=0911123624 |title = 黎明回家鄉個唱 稱心中永遠都有紅五星 |publisher = 北京晚報 |date = 2005-12-03 |accessdate = 2018-12-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181228174949/http://hk.crntt.com/crn-webapp/doc/docDetailCreate.jsp?coluid=21&kindid=267&docid=100067542&mdate=0911123624 |archive-date = 2018-12-28 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。黎新生是[[印尼華僑|印尼華僑]][[客家人|客家人]]，原籍[[廣東省|廣東省]][[梅縣|梅縣]]<ref>{{Cite book |title = 當代人，第1-12期 |location = 中國 |publisher = 當代人雜誌社 |date = 1993 |pages = 13|url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=uxJMAQAAIAAJ&q=%22%E7%A5%96%E7%B1%8D%22+%22%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%27%27%22 |language = zh-hans |accessdate = 2022-05-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220524120855/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=uxJMAQAAIAAJ&q=%22%E7%A5%96%E7%B1%8D%22+%22%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%27%27%22 |archive-date = 2022-05-24 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，1950年代成為中華人民共和國[[歸國華僑|歸國華僑]]，在北京讀大學並與當地人結婚，黎明是他的[[獨生子|獨生子]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://i.imgur.com/JZTv4Vk.jpg |title = 我的童年生活 |date = 1991-05-05 |publisher = 玉郎電視708期 |language = zh |accessdate = 2022-02-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220202001752/https://i.imgur.com/JZTv4Vk.jpg |archive-date = 2022-02-02 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，年幼時居於[[西城區|西城區]]羊肉[[胡同|胡同]]，主要由外祖母照顧<ref>{{Cite web |author = 提文靜 |url = http://www.chinanews.com/2002-09-16/26/223074.html |title = 黎明生在北京羊肉胡同 小時和外婆相依為命 |date = 2002-09-16 |publisher = 中國新聞網 |language = zh-hans |accessdate = 2020-03-01 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210222194259/http://www.chinanews.com/2002-09-16/26/223074.html |archive-date = 2021-02-22 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。當時印尼歸國華僑在[[無產階級文化大革命|無產階級文化大革命]]中受批鬥<ref>{{Cite book |author = Glen Peterson |title = Overseas Chinese in the People's Republic of China |location = London |publisher = Routledge |date = 2011 |pages = 163－178 |ISBN = 9781136638572|language = en}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |author = Glen Peterson |editor = 張茂榮翻譯 |title = 中華人民共和國的歸僑 |location = 香港 |publisher = 印尼民族建設基金會、香港印尼研究學社 |date = 2016 |ISBN = 9789881492630 |language = zh}}</ref>，黎明年約四歲時隨父親移民到[[英屬香港|英屬香港]]，曾就讀便以利小學、香港漢文師範同學會附屬學校<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://drive.google.com/file/d/1w3ZCwBsIllWGVPWDVU8AKBIjq2m32reS/view?usp=sharing |title =一九七九年上午校六丁班畢業照 |date = 1979 |publisher = 香港漢文師範同學會附屬學校 |language = zh |quote = 由下至上，第三行左四者是黎明 |accessdate = 2019-02-27 |archive-date = 2019-03-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190321103440/https://drive.google.com/file/d/1w3ZCwBsIllWGVPWDVU8AKBIjq2m32reS/view?usp=sharing |dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = https://drive.google.com/file/d/1jw2TqYapll7vEauTlZjb1NVkug1gKYom/view?usp=sharing |title = 一九七九年畢業典禮特刊－第廿一屆上午校六丁班 |date = 1979 |publisher = 香港漢文師範同學會附屬學校 |language = zh |accessdate = 2019-02-27 |archive-date = 2019-03-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190321103440/https://drive.google.com/file/d/1jw2TqYapll7vEauTlZjb1NVkug1gKYom/view?usp=sharing |dead-url = no}}</ref>及[[萃華英文書院|萃華英文書院]]<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20120514/50086623 |title = 黎明或為萃華演唱會表演 |publisher = 蘋果日報 |date = 2012-05-14 |accessdate = 2018-12-29 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181229075626/https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20120514/50086623 |archive-date = 2018-12-29 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，14歲時父親安排他到[[倫敦|倫敦]]寄宿留學<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://i.imgur.com/rhFZkAC.jpg |title = 抹不掉的成長烙印 |date = 1996-07-19 |publisher = 凸周刊 |language = zh |accessdate = 2021-06-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210610124958/https://i.imgur.com/rhFZkAC.jpg |archive-date = 2021-06-10 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，先後入讀Christ's College<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://i.imgur.com/mbeMsGT.jpg |title = 重返倫敦母校探訪 |date = 1996 |publisher = 電視周刊 |language = zh |quote = 展開歐、美巡迴演唱，此行我可順道往倫敦的母校CHRIST COLLEGE探訪一下了。|accessdate = 2021-06-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210609122340/https://i.imgur.com/mbeMsGT.jpg |archive-date = 2021-06-09 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>及King's Way Princeton College<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.peoplemaven.com/l/LgVeyP/Famous-Alumni-Westminster-Kingsway-College-(Camden%2C-UK) |title = Famous Alumni Westminster Kingsway College（Camden, UK）|publisher = www.peoplemaven.com |language =en |accessdate = 2019-02-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190222041845/https://www.peoplemaven.com/l/LgVeyP/Famous-Alumni-Westminster-Kingsway-College-(Camden%2C-UK) |archive-date = 2019-02-22 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。1985年，黎明從英國回流香港，曾任職電話推銷員及汽車經紀<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20141102/00282_002.html |title = 回到未紅時 |publisher = 東方日報 |date = 2014-11-02 |accessdate = 2020-03-31 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20141105103058/https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20141102/00282_002.html |archive-date = 2014-11-05 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，並修讀藝員訓練班課程及擔任臨時演員<ref name="夜話港樂2">{{Cite book |author = 何言|title = 夜話港樂2─填詞人X天王巨星X勁歌金曲 |location = 香港 |publisher = 香港中和出版有限公司 |date = 2015-08 |pages = 194－205，155－160 |ISBN = 9789888284979 |language = zh}}</ref>，1986年透過歌唱比賽加入娛樂圈，入行初期仍兼任推銷員<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/vQmLi9N.jpg |title = 黎明兼職推銷員 |publisher = 大公報 |pages = 21 |date = 1986-12-05 |accessdate = 2022-04-17 |archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20220417124147/https://i.imgur.com/vQmLi9N.jpg |archive-date = 2022-04-17 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，協助經營流動電話生意的父親銷售產品，後來主力發展娛樂事業，在演藝界工作至今<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://i.imgur.com/FzMB4ZP.jpg |title = 黎明不靠父蔭賣電話 |author = 楊清 |date = 1990-02-22 |page = 28-29 |publisher = 香港電視 |language = zh |accessdate = 2021-06-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210610124851/https://i.imgur.com/FzMB4ZP.jpg |archive-date = 2021-06-10 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。2008年，黎明與[[樂基兒|樂基兒]]在[[拉斯維加斯|拉斯維加斯]]註冊結婚<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/art/20090830/13153091 |title = 賭城婚禮又一宗 黎明、樂基兒結婚鐵證 |publisher = 蘋果日報 |date = 2009-08-30 |accessdate = 2018-12-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181228174725/https://hk.appledaily.com/entertainment/art/20090830/13153091 |archive-date = 2018-12-28 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，其後於2012年發聲明離婚及於2018年直接當父親，撫養1名女兒<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20121004/00282_001.html |title = 黎明 樂基兒發聲明離婚 |publisher = 東方日報 |date = 2012-10-04 |accessdate = 2018-12-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20121105215911/http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20121004/00282_001.html |archive-date = 2012-11-05 |dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_585601_0 |title = 黎明照顧早產B女 武漢演唱會押後 |date = 2018-05-05 |publisher = 壹週刊 |language = zh |accessdate = 2021-04-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190709081127/https://nextplus.nextmedia.com/article/2_585601_0 |archive-date = 2019-07-09 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，男助手彭靄泉（子泉）是黎明求學時期的同學<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |author = 阿吉 |url = https://i.imgur.com/NBAI9A0.jpg |title = 黎明保母叫子泉 一睇便知是好人 |publisher = 明報 |date = 1995-10-03 |accessdate = 2022-06-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220617081822/https://i.imgur.com/NBAI9A0.jpg |archive-date = 2022-06-17 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，自1990年代初開始協助黎明處理各種事務<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |author = 騫平 |url = https://i.imgur.com/U6i2ez5.jpg |title = 助手子泉否認與黎明決裂 |publisher = 明報 |date = 2000-04-02 |accessdate = 2022-02-05 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220205115531/https://i.imgur.com/U6i2ez5.jpg |archive-date = 2022-02-05 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

== 音樂事業 ==
=== 成為歌手 ===
黎明於中學時期在合唱團唱中低音，後來曾在[[亞洲電視藝員訓練班|亞洲電視藝員訓練班]]跟歌唱家韋秀嫻學唱歌<ref name="碧泉新星">{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/PMBE04F.png |title = 明日之星廖淑霞和黎明 少年十八十九時 |publisher = 華僑日報 |pages = 18 |date = 1985-08-24 |accessdate = 2021-07-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210725082510/https://i.imgur.com/PMBE04F.png |archive-date = 2021-07-25 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。1986年，黎明以[[蔡楓華|蔡楓華]]原唱的歌曲〈絕對空虛〉參加《[[新秀歌唱大賽|新秀歌唱大賽]]》，起初遭到父親反對，要求他到英國繼續學業<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/TTnELH7.jpg |title = 父勸勿發明星夢 參賽新秀唔衰得 |publisher = 明報 |date = 1998-03-21 |accessdate = 2021-06-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210610124248/https://i.imgur.com/TTnELH7.jpg |archive-date = 2021-06-10 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，而評判之一的[[林燕妮|林燕妮]]認為黎明的觀眾緣好、可塑性大，因此給他最高分數<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |author = 林燕妮 |url = https://i.imgur.com/mg5drw6.jpg |title = 黎明的黎明 |publisher = 報章 |date = 1992 |accessdate = 2022-06-05 |archive-url = http://web.archive.org/web/20220605020145/https://i.imgur.com/mg5drw6.jpg |archive-date = 2022-06-05 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。黎明在決賽中獲得銅獎後<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/nKsNvgt.jpg |title = 文佩玲憑「夢伴」奪五周年金咪獎 許志安獲銀牌 黎明得銅牌 |publisher = 華僑日報 |pages = 1 |date = 1986-07-14 |accessdate = 2022-01-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210911224513/https://i.imgur.com/nKsNvgt.jpg |archive-date = 2021-07-25 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，與華星唱片和電視廣播有限公司（無綫電視）分別簽訂經理人和歌手合約<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/zdUklim.jpg |title = 黎明替美男子主持即影籌款 |publisher = 華僑日報 |pages = 14 |date = 1987-10-19 |accessdate = 2021-10-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211004060141/https://i.imgur.com/zdUklim.jpg |archive-date = 2021-10-04 |dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref name="歌星約">{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/UftdtjG.jpg |title = 與無線只簽歌星約 黎明不能在外拍劇 |publisher = 華僑日報 |pages = 21 |date = 1990-01-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211004061446/https://i.imgur.com/UftdtjG.jpg |archive-date = 2021-10-04 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，隨後在演出電視劇《[[男兒本色_(香港電視劇)|男兒本色]]》時，經同劇演員[[林俊賢|林俊賢]]介紹認識歌唱老師[[戴思聰|戴思聰]]，並透過[[戴蘊慧|戴蘊慧]]提出請教要求。戴思聰認為黎明外形好，若提升歌藝實力，便有條件成為歌手，因此答應向黎明傳授樂理知識及聲學基礎<ref name="星河回憶錄">{{Cite book |author = 戴思聰 |title = 星河回憶錄 |pages = 75－107 |location = 香港 |publisher = 花千樹出版有限公司 |date = 2011-07 |ISBN = 9620756126 |language = zh}}</ref>。華星唱片曾經安排黎明到酒廊唱歌<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://i.imgur.com/n2ANkUw.jpg |title = 酒廊廣告 |date = 1987 |publisher = 富麗華牛扒酒廊 |language = zh |accessdate = 2021-06-11 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210611123309/https://i.imgur.com/n2ANkUw.jpg |archive-date = 2021-06-11 |dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = https://i.imgur.com/GDw0vQF.jpg |title = 酒廊廣告 |date = 1987 |publisher = 新麗晶餐廳酒廊 |language = zh |accessdate = 2021-06-11 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210611123541/https://i.imgur.com/GDw0vQF.jpg |archive-date = 2021-06-11 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，以及主唱電視劇歌曲，但未有為他發行唱片<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/ZWY4sIQ.jpg |title = 黎明真情流露喜形於色 |publisher = 華僑日報 |pages = 20 |date = 1990-08-17 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211004063248/https://i.imgur.com/ZWY4sIQ.jpg |archive-date = 2021-10-04 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，黎明的好友鄭萬橋有見及此，計劃斥資20萬元港幣，讓黎明以自資形式出版唱片，惟當時黎明與華星唱片仍有合約關係，加上缺乏宣傳資金，計劃因此擱置<ref name="星河回憶錄"/>。1989年，戴思聰推薦黎明到[[寶麗金|寶麗金]]試音<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://dailynews.sina.com/bg/ent/hktwstar/kwongwah/20100719/00071664608.html |title = 捧星有一手 戴思聰甘為黎明坐牢 |date = 2010-07-19 |publisher = 光華日報 |language = zh |accessdate = 2018-12-31 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181231194237/http://dailynews.sina.com/bg/ent/hktwstar/kwongwah/20100719/00071664608.html |archive-date = 2018-12-31 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，唱片監製[[向雪懷|向雪懷]]認為黎明的形象吸引，唱片公司正缺乏這類型的歌手，加上黎明能說流利國語，有助唱片公司發展國語音樂市場，遂取錄黎明成為旗下歌手<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://comebacktolove.blogspot.com/2016/09/blog-post_27.html |title = 向雪懷談「遲來的春天」、「一生中最愛」，談黎明、張學友，談黃凱芹拒唱「如果這是情」 |date = 2005-10-26 |publisher = come back to love 80-90年代廣東歌 |language = zh |accessdate = 2020-02-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191011130305/http://comebacktolove.blogspot.com/2016/09/blog-post_27.html |archive-date = 2019-10-11 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。

=== 早年發展 ===
隨着1980年代的香港歌手相繼淡出樂壇，唱片公司將發展焦點轉移到新晉歌手<ref name="流聲">{{Cite book |author = 黃志淙 |title = 流聲 |location = 香港|publisher = 香港特別行政區政府民政事務局 |date = 2007-01 |pages = 72－73 |ISBN = 9789620203664 |language = zh}}</ref>，1990年7月6日，寶麗金為黎明發行首張粵語專輯《[[Leon_(專輯)|Leon]]》<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.881903.com/highlight/2345051/ |title = 7月6日之廣東歌 |date = 2020-07-05 |publisher = 商業電台 |language = zh |accessdate = 2022-05-24 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220318202256/https://www.881903.com/highlight/2345051/廣東爆谷-明日之廣東歌/7月6日之廣東歌 |archive-date = 2022-03-18 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，在發行當天已獲得[[金唱片|金唱片]]銷量<ref name="黎明回憶錄">{{Cite web |url = https://i.imgur.com/XW0tz9N.jpg |title = 黎明事業終於見黎明 |author = 黎明、賈偉南 |date = 1992 |publisher = 黎明回憶錄 |language = zh |accessdate = 2021-11-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210509074439/https://i.imgur.com/XW0tz9N.jpg |archive-date = 2021-05-09 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，黎明憑此專輯獲得多項新人獎，打開了知名度<ref>{{Cite book |title = 香港人名錄 |publisher = 海南出版社 |date = 1997 |pages = 316 |url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=GTFB82BePS4C&q=%22%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%22+%22%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%BA%E7%8D%8E%22 |language = zh |accessdate = 2020-04-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190602235717/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=GTFB82BePS4C&q=%22%E9%BB%8E%E6%98%8E%22+%22%E6%96%B0%E4%BA%BA%E7%8D%8E%22 |archive-date = 2019-06-02 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。黎明於1991年初發行的第二張專輯《[[親近你|親近你]]》被視為力作<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |author = 劉存孝 |url = http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1939912/ |title = 黎天王登基前力作 |publisher = 星島日報 |date = 2019-01-04 |accessdate = 2021-05-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191007115018/http://std.stheadline.com/daily/article/detail/1939912/日報-副刊-黎天王登基前力作──回音地帶-劉存孝 |archive-date = 2019-10-07 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，銷量達到十萬張以上<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/fy2IDRO.jpg |title = 靚仔小生黎明 唱片得雙白金 他盼望可影視歌三線發展 |publisher = 大公報 |pages = 18 |date = 1991-02-02 |accessdate = 2021-10-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211004082440/https://i.imgur.com/fy2IDRO.jpg |archive-date = 2021-10-04 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，當中收錄的電視劇插曲〈如果這是情〉受到公眾注意<ref>{{Cite news |language = zh |author = 史順宜 |url = https://www.hk01.com/眾樂迷/110810/ |title = 黎明《如果這是情》冧盡80後「讓我美夢換你一世情」 |publisher = 香港01 |date = 2017-08-09 |accessdate = 2018-12-31 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190101051530/https://www.hk01.com/眾樂迷/110810/一首歌-黎明-如果這是情-冧盡80後-讓我美夢換你一世情 |archive-date = 2019-01-01 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，而接下來推出的《[[是愛、是緣|是愛、是緣]]》更成為1991年度[[IFPI香港唱片銷量大獎|IFPI香港唱片銷量大獎]]全年最高銷量大碟，主打歌曲〈對不起，我愛你〉登上香港各大音樂流行榜的冠軍位置<ref name="百歌爭鳴">{{Cite book |author = 林玉鑫 |title = 百歌爭鳴 成名曲、流行曲快樂大放送 |location = 中國 |publisher = 北京海潮出版社 | date = 2001-01|pages = 371|ISBN =7801512839 |language = zh}}</ref>。1991年7月，黎明參與《[[忘我大匯演|演藝界總動員忘我大滙演]]》，即場獲贊助港幣50萬元演唱〈對不起，我愛你〉，他在匆忙回到現場兼毫無準備的情況下，在現場琴手起音時入錯調，導致演唱失準<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://i.imgur.com/MllpxOT.jpg |title = 現場走音 耿耿於懷 |author = 黎明、賈偉南 |date = 1992 |publisher = 黎明回憶錄 |language = zh |accessdate = 2022-02-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220202020933/https://i.imgur.com/MllpxOT.jpg |archive-date = 2022-02-02 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，外界一方面認為黎明當時歌唱實力不足<ref>{{Cite news |language = zh |url = https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20170513/20019819 |title = 91年唱《對不起我愛你》失手 黎明自認唔夠經驗 |publisher = 蘋果日報 |date = 2017-05-13 |accessdate = 2019-01-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190102193500/https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20170513/20019819 |archive-date = 2019-01-02 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，另一方面則認為是無心之失<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://yuppiemusic.com/blog/f.htm |title =「走音天王」？為黎明走音大平反 |date = 2016-06-04 |publisher = yuppiemusic.com |language = zh |accessdate = 2019-01-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190102193508/http://yuppiemusic.com/blog/f.htm |archive-date = 2019-01-02 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，事件使到輿論對他的批評達致高峰，同時亦推高了他的人氣<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://michaelchu-73917.medium.com/黎明系列2-對不起-我愛你-對不起-我走音-34c30acc57a2 |title = 《對不起 我愛你》對不起 我走音 |author = 朱米高 |date = 2018-07-30 |publisher = 千千闋歌與我常在 |language = zh |accessdate = 2020-12-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20201204211802/https://michaelchu-73917.medium.com/黎明系列2-對不起-我愛你-對不起-我走音-34c30acc57a2 |archive-date = 2020-12-04 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。從1992年夏季開始，黎明被香港媒體稱作「四大天王」之一，填補了1980年代歌手引退後的真空位置<ref name="四大天王"/>。1993年，黎明在《[[十大勁歌金曲頒獎典禮|十大勁歌金曲頒獎典禮]]》從曾經提攜他的[[張國榮|張國榮]]手中領取「最受歡迎男歌手」獎，他認為首次獲得該獎項有很大鼓勵作用，也是他事業的新開始<ref>{{Cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/Dgd5wig.jpg |title = 獲得獎後感到鼓舞 黎明自我要求更高 |publisher = 報章 |date =1994-01-18 |accessdate = 2021-06-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210616125613/https://i.imgur.com/Dgd5wig.jpg |archive-date = 2021-06-16 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。
