=== 海外音樂市場 ===
1989年，黎明應邀到[[台灣|台灣]]演出電視劇《[[風雲時代|風雲時代]]》並主唱該劇插曲〈風雲塵煙〉，一度引起關注<ref>{{Cite book |author = 朱耀偉 |title = Hong Kong Cantopop: A Concise History |location = 香港 |publisher = 香港大學出版社 |date = 2017 |pages = 112 |ISBN = 9789888390588 |url = https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=62I2DwAAQBAJ&pg=PA112&lpg#v=onepage&q&f=false |language = en |accessdate = 2021-08-01 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191101123033/http://web.archive.org/screenshot/https://books.google.com.hk/books?id=62I2DwAAQBAJ&pg=PA112&lpg=PA112&dq=%22%E9%A2%A8%E9%9B%B2%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%22%2B%22%E9%A2%A8%E9%9B%B2%E5%A1%B5%E7%85%99%22&source=bl&ots=Rl-koCtqDZ&sig=ACfU3U0kNLDBU2Sfq2ZBQr8FVKLjboATQg&hl=zh-TW&sa=X&ved=2ahUKEwjOovC3_8jlAhUvyosBHfz-BVIQ6AEwCHoECAkQAQ#v=onepage&q&f=false |archive-date = 2019-11-01 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。1991年5月，黎明發行首張國語專輯《[[今夜妳會不會來|今夜妳會不會來]]》，由此打開台灣市場，專輯在台灣推出3天已獲得約十萬張銷量<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/J3r5YMj.jpg |title = 國語唱碟台銷十萬 黎明否認是其天下 |publisher = 大公報 |pages = 16 |date = 1991-07-07 |accessdate = 2021-10-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211006070542/https://i.imgur.com/J3r5YMj.jpg |archive-date = 2021-10-06 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，同名主打歌曲〈今夜妳會不會來〉登上台灣音樂流行榜冠軍位置<ref>{{Cite news |language = zh |author = 王祖壽 |url = https://i.imgur.com/mnclg9r.jpg |title = 黑馬黎明封王 總分勝一籌榜上寫新局 |publisher = 民生報 |date = 1991 |accessdate = 2021-06-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210530031623/https://i.imgur.com/mnclg9r.jpg |archive-date=2021-05-30 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。1995年，黎明在韓國推出國語專輯《[[愛難求_(黎明)|愛難求]]》，首次登上韓國音樂綜藝節目的舞台，他在1998年至1999年間推出主打歌曲時，亦另行推出韓語版本<ref name="樂觀韓流">{{Cite web |url = https://news.now.com/home/life/player?newsId=177825 |title = 樂觀韓流：黎明 迷倒韓國粉絲的香港巨星 |author = 鍾樂偉 |date = 2016-05-05 |publisher = Now新聞 |language = zh |accessdate = 2019-01-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181116132004/https://news.now.com/home/life/player?newsId=177825 |archive-date = 2018-11-16 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，同時亦曾於日本發行唱片<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://i.imgur.com/FfaC5nu.jpg |title = Channel L |date = 1999 |publisher = Leon Family（Japan）|language = ja |accessdate = 2021-08-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210802125217/https://i.imgur.com/FfaC5nu.jpg |archive-date = 2021-08-02 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。1998年，黎明憑歌曲〈我這樣愛你〉的韓語版本〈사랑한 후에〉（After Loving You）登上[[SBS_(韓國)|SBS電視台]]的音樂龍虎榜第4位<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://i.imgur.com/wlYnSaG.jpg |title = 黎明踩入韓國SBC電視台 |date = 1998-07 |publisher = 東方新地 |language = zh |accessdate = 2021-08-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210803052020/https://i.imgur.com/wlYnSaG.jpg |archive-date = 2021-08-03 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，成為首個登上韓國音樂流行榜前十名的海外歌手<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/a66YTMa.jpg |title = 黎明同舊機場講拜拜 500 Fans圍觀釀騷動 |publisher = 報章 |date = 1998-07-05 |accessdate = 2022-03-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220309053202/https://i.imgur.com/a66YTMa.jpg |archive-date = 2022-03-09 |dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite book |author = Yiu-Wai Chu |title = Hong Kong Cantopop: A Concise History |location = Hong Kong | publisher = Hong Kong University Press |date = 2017-01-01 |pages = 211 |ISBN = 9789888390588 |accessdate = 2021-10-30 |url = https://hkupress.hku.hk/pro/con/1611.pdf |language = en|quote = Leon Lai's Korean song “After Loving You” reaches top 10 on Korean pop charts, the first time a Hong Kong singer has managed to achieve this. |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20200920233423/https://hkupress.hku.hk/pro/con/1611.pdf |archive-date = 2020-09-20 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

=== 風格演變 ===
1990年代初，[[陳永明_(音樂人)|陳永明]]是黎明的唱片監製，他認為黎明適合演繹旋律簡單，亦有深度和層次的歌曲，而當時能夠發揮黎明演繹方法的香港作曲家不多，因此在1990年至1993年間以選唱外語改編歌曲為主<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://img9.doubanio.com/view/group_topic/l/public/p83406940.webp |title = 人物專訪 陳永明 |publisher = 黎明家族會刊第12期 |date = 1994-06 |language = zh |accessdate = 2021-08-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210804131031/https://img9.doubanio.com/view/group_topic/l/public/p83406940.webp |archive-date = 2021-08-04 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，常以斯文大方的形象演繹深情慢歌<ref>{{Cite book |author = 黃國恩 |title = 我們的四大天王──九十年代樂壇風光 |location = 香港 |publisher = 非凡出版 |date = 2020-07 |pages = 97 |ISBN = 9789888676002 |language = zh}}</ref>。1994年，黎明主唱的廣告歌曲〈[[那有一天不想你|那有一天不想你]]〉在各大音樂頒獎禮獲得多項大獎，廣告歌曲年代由此揭開序幕，隨後數年推出了多首同一系列的廣告歌曲，使他的事業發展更上一層樓<ref>{{Cite book |author = 黃志華、朱耀偉 |title = 香港歌詞八十談 |location = 香港 |publisher = 匯智出版有限公司 |date = 2011-09 |pages = 268－271 |ISBN = 9789881961952 |language = zh}}</ref>。1995年，[[香港商業電台|香港商業電台]]提倡「原創歌運動」，不播放非原創作品，鼓勵本地創作，此舉影響了唱片公司的製作方向，黎明選唱的歌曲亦轉為以香港本地作品為主<ref>{{Cite book |author = 朱耀偉|title = 音樂敢言之二－香港「原創歌運動」研究 |location = 香港 |publisher = Bestever Consultants Ltd. |date = 2004-08 |ISBN = 9789889795320 |language = zh}}</ref><ref name="香港音樂史論">{{Cite book |author = 劉靖之 |title =香港音樂史論：粵語流行典‧嚴肅音樂‧粵劇 |location = 香港 |publisher = 商務（香港）印書館 |date = 2013 |ISBN = 9620756126 |language = zh}}</ref>，同年，黎明拜訪北京[[中國音樂學院|中國音樂學院]]聲學系主任[[金鐵霖|金鐵霖]]，學習樂理、古典音樂和發聲技巧<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://i.imgur.com/qGMYRAQ.jpg |title = 黎明北京學藝有成績 |date = 1995-07-15 |publisher = 大眾電視第1055期 |language = zh |accessdate = 2020-02-15 |archive-date = 2020-02-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210805065912/https://i.imgur.com/qGMYRAQ.jpg |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，其後動手術割除位於聲帶的粉瘤，唱歌時感覺較以往舒適<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://i.imgur.com/2gFGwRT.jpg |title = 割粉瘤、廣音域 學聲樂有成績 |date = 1996-04-05 |publisher = 大眾電視1093期 |language = zh |accessdate = 2022-05-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210805070110/https://i.imgur.com/2gFGwRT.jpg |archive-date = 2021-08-05 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，並參考[[音樂製作人|音樂製作人]][[陳子鴻|陳子鴻]]的建議，嘗試改變自己唱歌的嗓音<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |author = 梁鴻斌 |url = https://i.imgur.com/SyLI2jM.jpg |title = 陳子鴻助他開嗓散發男人味 黎明動刀改變未來 |publisher = 大成報 |date = 1996-05-11 |accessdate = 2020-04-09 |archive-date = 2020-09-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210805065509/https://i.imgur.com/SyLI2jM.jpg |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

1996年，黎明的經理人[[陳善之|陳善之]]透過填詞人[[潘源良|潘源良]]，邀請[[雷頌德|雷頌德]]加盟黎明的唱片製作團隊<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.mpweekly.com/entertainment/interview/集體回憶/20160319-8688 |title = 「用最大勇氣支持他玩命」陳善之回首前塵四十載（十九）|date = 2016-03-19 |publisher = 明報周刊 |language = zh |accessdate =2021-11-06 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210121140758/https://www.mpweekly.com/entertainment/interview/集體回憶/20160319-8688 |archive-date = 2021-01-21 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，在歌曲創作和演繹方面加入新元素<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://app4.rthk.hk/special/goldsong2017/article.php?eid=54 |title = 雷頌德談流行曲的成功元素 |author = 陳穎洪 |date = 2017-12-08 |publisher = 香港電台 |language = zh |accessdate = 2018-12-31 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181231194124/http://app4.rthk.hk/special/goldsong2017/article.php?eid=54 |archive-date = 2018-12-31 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，黎明與雷頌德在音樂上找到共識，成為好友和合作夥伴<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |author = 小風 |url = https://i.imgur.com/bmmWjUg.jpg |title = 接受日雜誌訪問 黎明談兩個得力男人 |publisher = 明報 |date = 1997-05-13 |accessdate = 2021-06-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210610125443/https://i.imgur.com/bmmWjUg.jpg |archive-date = 2021-06-10 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，歌曲〈[[情深說話未曾講|情深說話未曾講]]〉被認為是他們合作的首個代表作品<ref name="香港音樂史論"/>。1997年，黎明推出首張以電子音樂為主的專輯《[[Leon_Sound|Leon Sound]]》，由雷頌德包辦整張專輯的製作，採用不同類型的電子音樂及以不同的唱腔演繹，在當時的香港流行樂壇屬罕見和前衛，但由於黎明與寶麗金的合約即將結束，該專輯不獲唱片公司重視，亦未有受到公眾注意<ref name="夜話港樂2"/>。1998年3月23日，黎明加盟[[新力唱片|新力唱片]]香港分部，以重質不重量為發展原則<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |author = 依玲 |url = https://i.imgur.com/Gi1TIpa.jpg |title = 新力大破慳囊 簽約儀式耗三百萬 黎明秘密練兵鞏固地位 |publisher = 明報 |date = 1998-03-24 |accessdate = 2021-08-03 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210803063843/https://i.imgur.com/Gi1TIpa.jpg |archive-date = 2021-08-03 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，雷頌德是他主要的搭檔<ref name="陳善之"/>，歌路以情歌和電子音樂舞曲為主，在曲風和演繹方面作出了調整，採用美式舞曲的音樂節奏，配合黎明的聲線，使到作品更為迎合大眾的喜好<ref name="夜話港樂2"/>。1998年至1999年間，黎明的音樂專輯《[[如果可以再見你|如果可以再見你]]》、《[[Leon_Now|Leon Now]]》、《[[眼睛想旅行|眼睛想旅行]]》同時登上全年唱片銷量排行榜前十名，並包攬冠、亞軍<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/ArSuRPJ.jpg |title = 全年唱片銷量前十位排名 |publisher = 報章|date = 2000 |accessdate = 2022-02-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220204120534/https://i.imgur.com/ArSuRPJ.jpg |archive-date = 2022-02-04 |dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://eladies.sina.com.cn/movie/news/movie/1999-12-06/15318.shtml |title = 香港唱片年銷量 黎明憑藉三碟稱王 |date = 1999-12-06 |publisher = 羊城晚報 |language = zh-hans |accessdate = 2018-12-31 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181231194221/http://eladies.sina.com.cn/movie/news/movie/1999-12-06/15318.shtml |archive-date = 2018-12-31 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。黎明認為香港流行音樂市場缺乏令人聞歌起舞的作品，並提議雷頌德跟他到韓國考察當地娛樂場所，藉此尋找流行音樂靈感，創作出迎合亞洲人喜好的舞曲<ref>{{Cite news |language = zh |author = 洪曉璇 |url = https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/115913/ |title = 黎明洗腦電音原來係向Kpop取經 晚晚捉雷頌德落首爾夜場蒲住學習 |publisher = 香港01 |date = 2017-08-31 |accessdate = 2019-01-01 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190101193805/https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/115913/黎明洗腦電音原來係向kpop取經-晚晚捉雷頌德落首爾夜場蒲住學習 |archive-date = 2019-01-01 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，其後在2000年推出的專輯《[[北京站_(黎明專輯)|北京站]]》作出新嘗試，在歌曲〈全日愛〉的前奏加入與中國國歌極為相似的旋律，引起大眾的討論<ref>{{Cite news |language = zh |author = 向樂高 |url = https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/115296/ |title = 雷頌德曾稱：擺明玩國歌 網民擔心黎明《全日愛》違法 |publisher = 香港01 |date = 2017-08-29 |accessdate = 2019-03-10 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181110040629/https://www.hk01.com/熱爆話題/115296/國歌法-雷頌德曾稱-擺明玩國歌-網民擔心黎明-全日愛-違法 |archive-date = 2018-11-10 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，此專輯的歌曲成為當年香港舞廳的熱門電音舞曲之一<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |author = 王嘉政 |url = https://www.hk01.com/藝文/101409/ |title = 回帶黎明玩串國歌 侮辱指責引發97電音革命 |publisher = 香港01 |date = 2017-06-30 |accessdate = 2019-12-12 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181110040625/https://www.hk01.com/藝文/101409/回歸廿年-回帶黎明玩串國歌-侮辱指責引發97電音革命 |archive-date = 2018-11-10 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。

