1991年，黎明以「天濛光」為筆名<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |author = 劉存孝 |url = https://i.imgur.com/Gqa8S0I.jpg |title = 「天濛光」首度登場 |publisher = 星島日報 |date = 2021-07-17 |accessdate = 2021-08-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210724073426/https://i.imgur.com/Gqa8S0I.jpg |archive-date = 2021-07-24 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，首次創作歌曲〈我的感覺〉，並於填詞方面參與意見，當時他表示希望籌建一所製作公司，從事音樂或電影的幕後製作<ref>{{Cite book |author = 則夫 |title = 黎明 Cover Story |location = 香港 |publisher = Music Express雜誌 |date = 1991 |pages = 4－5 |accessdate = 2021-08-08 |url = https://i.imgur.com/Qtdm574.jpg |language = zh |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210807225529/https://i.imgur.com/Qtdm574.jpg |archive-date = 2021-08-08 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，他認為音樂是無分國界，不應介懷選唱的歌曲是否香港原創音樂，但同時表明支持本地創作，亦會嘗試作曲及填詞<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/Y35HZKI.jpg |title = 有感創作人少新歌產量有限 黎明表態支持原創音樂 不惜身體力行作曲填詞 |publisher = 新報 |date = 1994 |accessdate = 2021-08-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210807011336/https://i.imgur.com/Y35HZKI.jpg |archive-date = 2021-08-07 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。1999年，黎明首次以導演身份（別名L.L.）自導自演拍攝歌曲《酸》的音樂短片<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/s38WWVT.jpg |title = 黎明不介意攞唔到銷量大獎 |publisher = 太陽報 |date = 2001-01-19 |accessdate = 2021-08-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210807021636/https://i.imgur.com/s38WWVT.jpg |archive-date = 2021-08-07 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，在隨後的一年多曾為十多部音樂短片執導<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/VaYvHUq.jpg |title = 北京站銷量冠軍竟榜上無名 我冇報數之嘛 |publisher = 東方日報 |date = 2001-01-19 |accessdate = 2021-08-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210807061056/https://i.imgur.com/VaYvHUq.jpg |archive-date = 2021-08-07 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，2002年獲邀為[[國際足協世界盃|世界盃]]大中國區主唱官方主題曲〈衝鋒陷陣〉及執導拍攝此歌曲的音樂短片<ref name="多重奏">{{Cite book |author = 周耀輝、高偉雲 |title = 多重奏: 香港流行音樂聲像的全球流動 |location = 香港|publisher = 香港中文大學出版社 |date = 2015 |ISBN = 9629965879 |language = zh}}</ref>。

2004年，黎明以合夥人身份與[[林建岳|林建岳]]合作成立[[東亞唱片_(製作)|東亞唱片製作有限公司]]（A Music）<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20040729/4204229 |title = 成立唱片製作公司做老闆 |publisher = 蘋果日報 |date = 2004-07-29 |accessdate = 2019-01-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190121175202/https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20040729/4204229 |archive-date = 2019-01-21 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，除了加盟成為旗下歌手，亦參與歌曲概念和音樂短片製作，他表示投資成立唱片公司，是希望有新嘗試和更大的發展空間，發掘熱愛音樂的新人<ref>{{cite web |url = http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/4/7/31/n613245.htm |title = 黎明當老板開拓更大空間 發掘熱愛音樂的新人 |date = 2004-07-31 |publisher = 大紀元時報 |language = zh |accessdate = 2019-01-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190121232649/http://www.epochtimes.com/b5/4/7/31/n613245.htm |archive-date = 2019-01-21 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。黎明於2011年執導拍攝《遲D見》音樂短片，使用[[三維空間|3D]]及[[CG作畫|CG作畫]]技術，以「真人頭、動畫身」方式呈現<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20110413/00282_010.html |title = 黎明掟300萬剪走JM金Bra |publisher = 東方日報 |date = 2011-04-13 |accessdate = 2021-08-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210807120355/https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20110413/00282_010.html |archive-date = 2021-08-07 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，獲得[[勁歌王金曲金榜|勁歌王金曲金榜]]的「最佳MV大獎」和「最佳MV導演大獎」<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://ent.sina.com.cn/y/2011-11-19/15543485379.shtml |title = 勁歌王頒獎禮揭曉 |publisher = 新浪音樂 |date = 2011-11-19 |language = zh-hans |accessdate = 2021-08-07|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160304142339/http://ent.sina.com.cn/y/2011-11-19/15543485379.shtml |archive-date = 2016-03-04 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，同年，黎明投資製作手機應用程式「樂Loop」，為用戶提供旗下歌手的音樂資訊<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |author = 葉雪 |url = https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20110628/15381394 |title = 黎明出App搵嘉欣合作 |publisher = 蘋果日報 |date = 2011-06-28 |accessdate = 2021-08-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190610154249/https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/entertainment/daily/article/20110628/15381394 |archive-date = 2019-06-10 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。2013年，黎明成立製作公司「Player One」，公司業務包括演唱會製作、售票等，曾於2017年舉辦大型戶外音樂節<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20161122/00282_024.html |title = 黎明打頭陣玩轉中環海濱 國際DJ歌手排隊Show Off |publisher = 東方日報 |date = 2016-11-22 |accessdate = 2021-08-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190616122848/https://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/entertainment/20161122/00282_024.html |archive-date = 2019-06-16 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。2019年，黎明以「[[明福俠|明福俠]]」身份與新進音樂單位合作創辦樂隊[[Gingerbread_(樂隊)|Gingerbread]]<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190430/1556626733312/ |title = 呼籲粉絲揀海報 黎明組樂隊：Band名叫Gingerbread |publisher = 明報 |date = 2019-04-30 |accessdate = 2019-05-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190509131505/https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190430/1556626733312/【呼籲粉絲揀海報】黎明組樂隊-band名叫gingerbread |archive-date = 2019-05-09 |dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://hd.stheadline.com/life/hotpicks/20210706/582255/live.php |title = 金句王開Show 你對黎明金曲認識有幾多？8大入場前必要識Leon冷門金曲 |publisher = 頭條日報 |date = 2021-07-06 |accessdate = 2021-08-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210706083946/https://hd.stheadline.com/life/hotpicks/20210706/582255/live.php |archive-date = 2021-07-06 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，他希望能創作不同的音樂文化，開闊大眾的視野<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |author = 彭嘉彬 |url = https://www.hk01.com/眾樂迷/365871/ |title = 黎明組樂隊Gingerbread　新作《勁傾心》改編Radias分享初戀往事 |publisher = 香港01 |date = 2019-08-20 |accessdate = 2019-08-20 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190820124455/https://www.hk01.com/眾樂迷/365871/黎明組樂隊gingerbread-新作-勁傾心-改編radias分享初戀往事 |archive-date = 2019-08-20 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。2010年代至今，黎明除了推出個人音樂作品外，亦首次與[[麥浚龍|麥浚龍]]、[[張敬軒|張敬軒]]等歌手在音樂領域上合作<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191031/60217217 |title = 麥浚龍搵黎明合作新歌《忘記和記》 大玩90年代曲風 |publisher = 蘋果日報 |date = 2019-10-31 |accessdate = 2021-08-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20191111032832/https://hk.entertainment.appledaily.com/enews/realtime/article/20191031/60217217 |archive-date = 2019-11-11 |dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://topick.hket.com/article/3027145/ |title = 黎明張敬軒MV點擊破100萬 Leon長文講跟軒仔合作感受 |publisher = 香港經濟日報 |date = 2021-08-08 |accessdate = 2021-08-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210808113051/https://topick.hket.com/article/3027145/ |archive-date = 2021-08-08 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，並鼓勵同業做好自己的本分，一起把音樂做好<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://news.mingpao.com/pns/娛樂/article/20220621/s00016/1655748634786/ |title = 黎明抛金句鼓勵做好音樂 |publisher = 明報 |date = 2022-06-21 |accessdate = 2022-06-21 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220621054456/https://news.mingpao.com/pns/娛樂/article/20220621/s00016/1655748634786/黎明抛金句鼓勵做好音樂-古天樂大灣區搭景拍科幻片《天梯》 |archive-date = 2022-06-21 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。

== 個人演唱會 ==
