===流行趨勢及文化===
1990年代初，黎明憑電視劇和唱片打開知名度<ref>{{Cite book |author = 陳怡東 |title = 當世事再沒完美：香港流行樂壇1974-2013 |location = 北京 |publisher = 法律出版社 |date = 2015 |pages = 第二章 |ISBN = 9787511880758 |language = zh |quote = 1990年因為TVB的電視劇和新出的唱片，黎明成為了樂壇的火熱男新人。不到一年香港就刮起黎明旋風}}</ref>，他主演的電視劇被視為具有收視保證的作品，成為大眾焦點<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/650136/ |title = 黎明係1990年代收視福將 兩套主演劇成年度冠軍 |publisher = 香港01 |author = 秦志鴻 |date = 2021-07-13 |accessdate = 2021-07-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210713230500/https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/650136/阿sir早晨-黎明係1990年代收視福將-兩套主演劇成年度冠軍 |archive-date = 2021-07-13 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，電視台曾先後多次播放他主演的作品<ref name="TVB周刊"/>，借助他的人氣來爭取收視<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/BF2SmoB.jpg |title = 無綫借《人在邊緣》挽劣勢 |publisher = 蘋果日報 |page = C04 |date = 2016-05-23 |accessdate = 2021-09-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210925123541/https://i.imgur.com/BF2SmoB.jpg |archive-date = 2021-09-25 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。黎明主唱的多首歌曲具有高傳唱度，在多年後仍然被視為金曲<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160306/bkn-20160306191212072-0306_00862_001.html |title = 黎明盛世屈晒機 |publisher = 東方日報 |date = 2016-03-06 |accessdate = 2021-09-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180131161248/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160306/bkn-20160306191212072-0306_00862_001.html |archive-date = 2018-01-31 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，他以前所屬的唱片公司常趁勢推出黎明的精選輯圖利<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = http://orientaldaily.on.cc/archive/20051021/ent/ent_a04cnt.html |title = 黎明出特別版大碟 舊公司爭飯食 |publisher = 東方日報 |date = 2005-10-21 |accessdate = 2021-09-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190224115824/http://orientaldaily.on.cc/archive/20051021/ent/ent_a04cnt.html |archive-date = 2019-02-24 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。1990年代中後期，黎明與雷頌德合作<ref>{{Cite news |language = zh |url = https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200507/1588848282439/ |title = 雷頌德被彈快歌唔掂 跟黎明起衝突 |publisher = 明報|date = 2020-05-07 |accessdate = 2020-05-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200508063828/https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20200507/1588848282439/靠郭富城省靚招牌-雷頌德被彈快歌唔掂-跟黎明起衝突 |archive-date = 2020-05-08 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，將香港的電子音樂水平提升到國際水準<ref name="夜話港樂2"/>，掀起了中文電子舞曲的潮流<ref>{{Cite news |language = zh |author = Jaguar |url = http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/adult/20040114/20040113235805_0014.html |title = 中文D歌進化史 |publisher = 太陽報 |date = 2004-01-14 |accessdate = 2019-01-01 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190101145408/http://the-sun.on.cc/channels/adult/20040114/20040113235805_0014.html |archive-date = 2019-01-01 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。1997年，黎明以牛仔褲造型演繹的純綿品牌廣告在韓國播出後，掀起了牛仔褲熱潮，當地的牛仔褲銷量在三個月內上升超過港幣五千萬元營業額，二十多個牛仔褲品牌爭相以黎明宣傳的純綿品牌來生產旗下產品<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/J4aLvWq.jpg |title = 黎明純棉廣告韓國播放 掀搶購牛仔褲熱潮 |publisher = 蘋果日報 |date = 1997 |accessdate = 2022-03-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220302121802/https://i.imgur.com/J4aLvWq.jpg |archive-date = 2022-03-02 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。傳媒指韓國娛樂公司在培訓當地藝人時，曾經參考香港藝人的衣著造型，部份韓國藝人的髮型和服裝跟黎明早年的造型相同<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20150620/bkn-20150620221119003-0620_00862_001.html |title = 網民熱話：黎明勁過K-pop 一早識玩電音 |publisher = 東方日報 |date = 2015-06-20 |accessdate = 2020-08-27 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180921051425/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20150620/bkn-20150620221119003-0620_00862_001.html |archive-date = 2018-09-21 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。出生於北京的黎明，在談理論時混合了普通話和廣東話文法<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://news.mingpao.com/ins/娛樂/article/20160315/s00007/1458052328815/ |title = 黎明唔覺金句好笑：我在談理論 |publisher = 明報 |date = 2016-03-15 |accessdate = 2021-09-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210926010307/https://news.mingpao.com/ins/娛樂/article/20160315/s00007/1458052328815/黎明唔覺金句好笑-我在談理論 |archive-date = 2021-09-26 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，被傳媒形容為「金句王」，部份詞句更成為[[流行語|流行語]]<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://topick.hket.com/article/2737908 |title = Leon教如何不空肚食早餐 黎明12大人生金句：坎坷過後有艇搭 |publisher = 香港經濟日報 |date = 2020-08-28 |accessdate = 2021-09-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210926024928/https://topick.hket.com/article/2737908 |archive-date = 2021-09-26 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。黎明自1993年開始與電訊公司長期合作，主唱廣告歌曲及演出廣告，自此，廣告歌曲與流行歌曲的商業結合，成為香港流行樂壇往後的一個經營模式，而在廣告製作上配合故事創作，並結合歌手形象，亦成為了當時的一個創新潮流<ref>{{Cite book |author = 黃國恩 |title = 我們的四大天王──九十年代樂壇風光 |location = 香港 |publisher = 非凡出版 |date = 2020-07 |pages = 93－94 |ISBN = 9789888676002 |language = zh}}</ref>，評論認為黎明昔日的作品，是1980年代和1990年代出生的人的[[集體回憶|集體回憶]]<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.ln.edu.hk/mcsln/criticism/70th-criticism/70th-criticism-06 |title= 從「毛記」看八九十後青少年的香港文化身份 |author = 陳惠珍 |date = 2018-05 |publisher = 嶺南大學 |language = zh |accessdate = 2021-09-26 |quote = 此廣告爆紅的原因黎明及廣告歌原曲是八九十後青年人的集體回憶 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210925022923/https://www.ln.edu.hk/mcsln/criticism/70th-criticism/70th-criticism-06 |archive-date = 2021-09-25 |dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160518/bkn-20160518010714102-0518_00862_001.html |title = 重播黎明經典神劇 網民齊玩集體回憶 |publisher = 東方日報 |date = 2016-05-18 |accessdate = 2019-10-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190605181304/https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20160518/bkn-20160518010714102-0518_00862_001.html |archive-date = 2019-06-05 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。

===大眾認同及追隨===
1990年代初，黎明被視為偶像派<ref>{{Cite book |author = 朱耀偉 |title = 歲月如歌－詞話香港粵語流行曲 |location = 香港 |publisher = 三聯書店（香港）有限公司 |date = 2009-09 |pages = 151－152，155－163 |ISBN = 9789620428807 |language =zh}}</ref>，傳媒於1992年視他為香港最受歡迎的四名男歌手之一，統稱「四大天王」<ref name="四大天王"/>，這個稱號得到廣泛市民認同<ref name="流聲"/>。黎明的歌迷及影迷主要來自香港、亞洲和全球華人社區，前南韓總統[[盧武鉉|盧武鉉]]於2003年在[[清華大學|清華大學]]的演講亦提及黎明在韓國是家喻戶曉的藝人<ref>{{Cite journal |author = TAE YOUNG KIM, DAL YONG JIN |url = https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/606b/f3b0d9ac639243a43e5555c48b9295fd50ac.pdf |title = Cultural Policy in the Korean Wave: An Analysis of Cultural Diplomacy Embedded in Presidential Speeches |journal = International Journal of Communication |year = 2016 |issue = 10 |pages = 10 |quote = Also, our youngsters are fond of Chinese movie stars like Zhang Yimou, Gong Li, and Leon Lai. |language = en |accessdate = 2020-02-25 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200225052903/https://pdfs.semanticscholar.org/606b/f3b0d9ac639243a43e5555c48b9295fd50ac.pdf |archive-date = 2020-02-25 |dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url = http://news.creaders.net/world/2003/07/09/big5/421791.html |title = 韓國總統盧武鉉在清華大學演講（全文）|date = 2003-07-09 |publisher = 萬維讀者網 |language = zh |accessdate = 2018-11-01 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181101055253/http://news.creaders.net/world/2003/07/09/big5/421791.html |archive-date = 2018-11-01 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。報導指歌迷及影迷對黎明的喜愛達到瘋狂程度，除了收集黎明的照片、剪報、參加歌迷會活動外，有人為了與黎明見面，甘願到電視城或偏僻的拍攝地點守候數小時<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/zOp4PNb.jpg |title = 青春偶像魅力沒法擋 青年迷戀程度達瘋狂 荒山野嶺苦候 那怕五、六小時 |publisher = 華僑日報 |pages = 24 |date = 2021-09-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210928020933/https://i.imgur.com/zOp4PNb.jpg |archive-date = 2021-09-28 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。不少女性視黎明為交往或結婚對象，願意為他生兒育女及終生等待他<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url =https://i.imgur.com/nzDA0KH.jpg |title = 有歌迷稱非他不嫁 黎明呼籲歌迷理智 |publisher = 大公報 |pages = 20 |date = 1991-08-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210928063411/https://i.imgur.com/nzDA0KH.jpg |archive-date = 2021-09-28 |dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/n3bxTKI.jpg |title = 洋女四十揚言包生仔 黎明存厚道不願置評 |publisher = 新報 |date = 1995 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210928064523/https://i.imgur.com/n3bxTKI.jpg |archive-date = 2021-09-28 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，也有人為黎明而自殺<ref>{{Cite book |author = 鄺小燕| title = 旭日初升 |location = 香港|publisher = 廣州出版社 |date = 1993 |ISBN = 7805920060 |accessdate = 2021-09-28 |url = https://i.imgur.com/ZlraJPY.jpg |language = zh-hans|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210928064123/https://i.imgur.com/ZlraJPY.jpg |archive-date = 2021-09-28 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。黎明的官方歌迷會「[[黎明家族|黎明家族]]」於1994年發展為國際組織，在多個國家及地區設立分社<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/IDIs0Oo.jpg |title = 黎明家族即將成立 歌迷國際化遍及美加台星韓 |publisher = 新報 |date = 1994 |accessdate = 2021-09-26 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210518121731/https://i.imgur.com/IDIs0Oo.jpg |archive-date = 2021-05-18 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，傳媒表示從任何頒獎禮上皆可感受到黎明歌迷團的氣勢，他們的瘋狂表現更甚於張國榮和譚詠麟年代的追星族<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/kvAh0Nz.jpg |title = 三大天王不相伯仲 |publisher = 明報 |date = 1995 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210928065758/https://i.imgur.com/kvAh0Nz.jpg |archive-date = 2021-09-28 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。2016年，黎明在演唱會牌照問題的危機處理表現獲得各界人士的認同和讚賞<ref>{{Cite book |author = 徐緣 |title = 關公災難 |location = 香港 |publisher = 白卷出版社 |date = 2016-07 |pages = 87－89 |ISBN = 9789887711919 |language = zh}}</ref>，一度形成俗稱「黎明效應」的社會效應<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1042381 |title = 黎明效應在香江 |author = 陸偉聰 |date = 2016-05-17 |publisher = 香港獨立媒體網 |language = zh |accessdate = 2021-09-28 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190119174419/https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1042381 |archive-date = 2019-01-19 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。有歌迷於2020年自行建立群組，凝聚不同年齡的歌迷，他們表示黎明能使人成長<ref>{{Cite news |language = zh |url = https://topick.hket.com/article/3102437/ |title = 港媽從13歲起迷戀黎明30年 重拾少女心追星應援：Leon令我們成長 |publisher = 香港經濟日報 |date = 2011-11-09 |accessdate = 2011-11-09 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211109074731/https://topick.hket.com/article/3102437/ |archive-date = 2021-11-09 |dead-url = no}}</ref>，認為黎明與歌迷之間是互相陪伴的關係，並表示在有生之年仍會追隨黎明<ref>{{Cite news |language = zh |author = 趙允琳 |url = https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/698219/|title = 追星成心靈寄託 姨姨粉認真程度不輸少女粉絲 |publisher = 香港01 |date = 2011-11-08 |accessdate = 2011-11-08 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211108120651/https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/698219/星期日檔案-追星成心靈寄託-姨姨粉認真程度不輸少女粉絲 |archive-date = 2011-11-08 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。監製[[林肯_(編導)|林肯]]認為黎明的說話有智慧而且有一套思維模式，能夠帶給年輕人心靈慰藉<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/690087/ |title = 連環拋黎明金句玩致敬 監製：聽落似亂蹹細嚼極有智慧 |publisher = 香港01 |date = 2021-10-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211020130621/https://www.hk01.com/即時娛樂/690087/青年心城-連環拋黎明金句玩致敬-監製-聽落似亂蹹細嚼極有智慧 |archive-date = 2021-10-18 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。

== 榮譽及獎項 ==
{{main|黎明獲獎與提名列表}}
從1990年直到1999年宣佈不再領取香港樂壇獎項為止，黎明獲得二百多個音樂獎項，包括連續9年獲得《[[十大中文金曲頒獎音樂會|十大中文金曲頒獎音樂會]]》[[十大中文金曲頒獎音樂會十大中文金曲獎|十大中文金曲獎]]及3度獲得[[十大中文金曲頒獎音樂會全球華人至尊金曲獎|全球華人至尊金曲獎]]；憑歌曲〈那有一天不想你〉、〈情深說話未曾講〉、〈只要為我愛一天〉和〈我這樣愛你〉先後4度獲得[[勁歌金曲頒獎典禮金曲金獎|勁歌金曲頒獎典禮金曲金獎]]，成為獲得該獎項最多的歌手之一，以及在7年間獲得《[[叱咤樂壇流行榜|叱咤樂壇流行榜]]頒獎典禮》的所有主要獎項<ref name="香港音樂史論"/>。影視方面，黎明曾獲得多個電影和廣告獎項<ref name="我地廣告"/>，包括於2002年憑電影《三更之回家》獲得金馬獎最佳男主角<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://www.goldenhorse.org.tw/awards/nw/?serach_type=award&sc=8&search_regist_year=2002&ins=32 |title = 第39屆金馬獎入圍得獎 |publisher = 台北金馬影展 |language = zh |accessdate = 2020-02-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181008214009/http://www.goldenhorse.org.tw/awards/nw/?serach_type=award&sc=10&search_regist_year=2002&ins=30 |archive-date = 2018-10-08 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。此外，黎明是首名持有高級官員使用的紅色聯合國通行證的華人<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://i.imgur.com/J45JbAe.jpg |title = 黎明獲頒特使級護照 |publisher = 東周刊 |date = 1995-12-13 |language = zh|accessdate = 2021-11-04 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210524125422/https://i.imgur.com/J45JbAe.jpg |archive-date = 2021-05-24 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，曾創下慈善活動受惠人數最多的健力士世界紀錄<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/DtQnNCC.jpg |title = 黎明榮登健力氏大全 |publisher = 蘋果日報 |date = 1995-12-11 |accessdate = 2021-05-24 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210524125714/https://i.imgur.com/DtQnNCC.jpg |archive-date = 2021-05-24 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。1994年，美國加州屋侖市和三藩市政府，分別將每年的10月15日及10月16日定為「黎明日」，以表彰黎明對慈善事業作出的貢獻<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/9oFFBLU.jpg |title = 黎明抵達三藩市 十六日定為「黎明日」 將步行金門橋籌款 |date = 1994 |accessdate = 2021-09-29 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20210929071429/https://i.imgur.com/9oFFBLU.jpg |archive-date = 2021-09-29 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。1998年，黎明獲選為「香港十大傑出青年」<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://toyp1.jcihk.org/past-hk-toyp-awardees/ |title = 歷屆香港傑青 |publisher = 國際青年商會香港總會 |language = zh |accessdate = 2019-01-18 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20180809183911/http://toyp1.jcihk.org/past-hk-toyp-awardees/ |archive-date = 2018-08-09 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，並先後於2003年獲「[[榮譽勳章|榮譽勳章]]」；2009年年獲「[[銅紫荊星章|銅紫荊星章]]」；2019年獲「[[銀紫荊星章|銀紫荊星章]]」<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190701/1561952092627/ |title = 第三度授勳 黎明獲銀紫荊星章 |publisher = 明報 |date = 2019-07-01 |accessdate = 2019-07-01 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190701062955/https://ol.mingpao.com/ldy/showbiz/latest/20190701/1561952092627/【第三度授勳】黎明獲銀紫荊星章-謝謝 |archive-date = 2019-07-01 |dead-url = no}}</ref>。

==音樂及影視作品==
{{main|黎明音樂作品列表|黎明歌曲列表|黎明影視作品列表}}
黎明在1980年代後期主唱的電視劇歌曲，是他最早期的音樂作品，當時華星唱片沒有為他推出個人唱片，直到1990年跳槽到寶麗金唱片公司後開始發行音樂專輯，早期的專輯大多以[[雷射唱片|雷射唱片]]、[[黑膠唱片|黑膠唱片]]和[[卡式錄音帶|卡式錄音帶]]形式推出，後來以雷射唱片為主<ref>{{Cite book |author = 陳怡東 |title = 當世事再沒完美：香港流行樂壇1974-2013 |location = 中國 |publisher = 法律出版社 |date = 2015 |ISBN = 9787511880758 |language = zh}}</ref>，他認為每張專輯都要有新元素帶給聽眾，因此他會在專輯籌備前參與工作會議，提出自己的意見<ref>{{Cite web |url = https://i.imgur.com/xZgzg0y.jpg |title = 最注重幕後質素與創作 Leon新唱片有很多突破 希望歌迷都感覺到進步 |date = 1993 |publisher = 大眾電視 |language = zh |accessdate = 2022-01-15 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20220115075908/https://i.imgur.com/xZgzg0y.jpg |archive-date = 2022-01-15 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。2011年，黎明首次發行數碼唱片，此後的音樂作品則主要透過網絡頻道與大眾分享<ref>{{Cite web |url = http://news.cntv.cn/20111104/108702.shtml |title = 黎明新碟市面不銷售 |date = 2018-02-09 |publisher = 中國網絡電視台 |language = zh |accessdate = 2019-03-02 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20181216163416/http://news.cntv.cn/20111104/108702.shtml |archive-date = 2018-12-16 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。黎明早年的影視作品以電視劇和電影為主，透過電視頻道、電影院播出，部份作品以錄影帶形式在香港或海外地區發行<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/B013Qvi.jpg |author = 朱侶 |title = 大馬的戲迷母親廿四孝 無線影帶市場不俗 |publisher = 華僑日報 |pages = 16 |date = 1991-07-21 |accessdate = 2021-10-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211007024406/https://i.imgur.com/B013Qvi.jpg |archive-date = 2021-10-07 |dead-url = yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/NOiHhvO.jpg |title = 黎明影帶受歡迎 台灣掀熱潮 |publisher = 華僑日報 |pages = 13 |date = 1991-09-03 |accessdate = 2021-10-07 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211007072810/https://i.imgur.com/NOiHhvO.jpg |archive-date = 2021-10-07 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>，自1990年代開始除了演出電影和電視劇，亦參演音樂特輯、音樂劇、電台廣播劇、網路劇等，2017年上映首部執導電影<ref>{{cite news |language = zh |url = https://i.imgur.com/8UPsLwd.jpg |title = 首次自導自演 黎明被爆愛打機 |publisher = 頭條日報 |pages = 47 |date = 2017-05-16 |accessdate = 2021-11-14 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20211114065356/https://i.imgur.com/8UPsLwd.jpg |archive-date = 2021-10-07 |dead-url = yes}}</ref>。

== 派台歌曲成績 ==
{{main|黎明派台歌曲成績列表}}
「派台歌」是指唱片公司在歌手推出新唱片的時候，將主要推銷的歌曲製成[[樣本唱片|樣本唱片]]，派發給媒體作宣傳用途<ref>{{Cite book |author = 黃夏柏 |title = 漫遊八十年代——聽廣東歌的好日子 |location = 香港 |publisher = 非凡出版 |date = 2017-10 |pages = 13, 50－60 |ISBN = 9888463136 |language = zh |quote = 近十年開始聽到「派台歌」之稱，記憶中以往並無此一詞。}}</ref>，「黎明派台歌曲成績列表」列出黎明歷年來的派台歌曲在香港五大電子媒體音樂流行榜的最高位置。

